Phase 0 â€” Target & Objective

Purpose: Prevent basic logic change

Task 0.1 - Write Down Objective Of CRM (1 word sentence)
 - To track internal company quotations and win rate

Task 0.2 - List down Out of scopes
 - No setting of user authorization
 - No do quotation automation
 - No domain, no open to public

Remark:
The purpose of this CRM is for tracking of sales quotation activities only. 
To present business analysis (quotation) effectiveness to management for continuous improvement.


Phase 1 â€” Data set and status design

Task 1.1 â€” List down all data to be collected/recorded

 1. Project Title (Standardize project title formula)
    - Project Title Name > Site Address
 2. Company Name
 3. Quotation No
 4. Quotation Version (revision_no)
 5. Quotation Status
 6. Date
 7. Validity end date (Default 30 days)

Task 1.2 â€” Define Quotation Revision Rules

 1. In which situation build new quotation - New project or new company or new quotation Version
 2. In which situation to change status - Receive PO, receive feedback of awarded to others or product unmatch
 3. Allow to delete quotation - No (This is a part of sales KPI)

Task 1.3 â€” Define status

 1. Quotation sent (Quotation sent out to client)
 2. Waiting for PO (client request for site visit/client disclose/shop drawings approve)
 3. Win 
 4. Lose (State Reason Of Lose)
 5. Cancelled (Received PO but Cancelled job)


Phase 2 â€” dataset definitation

Task 2.1

Transform all data collected as in phase 1 into dataset


Task 2.2 Confirm relationship

quotation â†’ project

quotation â†’ company

Task 2.3 Added below keyword

 - quotation.is_latest
 - quotation.revision_no
 - quotation.created_at
 - quotation.updated_at

Task 2.4 Explain revise quotation

 - Revision of quotation can be due to few reason:
  1. Sales quotation wrong
  2. Specs / Design change
  3. Request discount


